# This repo's whole point is the .cursor/ framework, but Cursor dirs are often
# ignored globally. Re-include it here, then re-ignore the one ADO file below.
!.cursor/

# `.cursor/ado/target.md` is the only file with your details in it (org, assignee,
# email), so it stays out of git. You create it from ado/target.example.md only if
# you turn ADO on. Everything else — including your todo files — IS tracked: make
# your repo private if you want your list kept private.
.cursor/ado/target.md
